Deutsche Bank AG (DBK) ’s Christian Ricken
will join the bank’s 17-member executive committee,  Der Spiegel 
reported, without saying where it got the information.  Ricken, 45, is to work mainly on the integration of
Deutsche Postbank AG, the magazine said.  To contact the reporter for this story:
